<section class="section ways" id="ways">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="ways__head">
      <span class="eyebrow">The Next Faithful Step</span>
      <h2>Three ways your church <em>partners</em> with us.</h2>
    </div>

    <!-- 01 PRAYER -->
    <article class="way" id="pray">
      <div class="way__num">PRAYER<strong>01</strong></div>
      <div class="way__body">
        <h3>Pray <em>for</em> the nations.</h3>
        <p>The first faithful step is intercession. Stand with our missionaries, our movements, and the Lord's work across Africa.</p>
        <ul class="way__list">
          <li>Pray for <strong>Uganda's House of Prayer for All Nations</strong> to be mightily used by the LORD in prayer and intercession for Christ's mission.</li>
          <li>Pray for the Muslim-dominated country of <strong>Chad</strong>, the final construction and licensing of the new Favor FM radio station, and the Christian broadcasting that will reach western Chad and eastern Nigeria.</li>
          <li>Pray for this spring's season of <strong>Portable Bible Schools</strong> that will offer Christ, create discipleship communities, and train leaders who make disciples.</li>
          <li>Pray for war to cease and <strong>peace to flourish across the Sahel</strong>.</li>
        </ul>
        <a class="way__cta" href="https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=LHarkRULU7Q" target="_blank" rel="noopener">
          <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="currentColor" aria-hidden="true"><polygon points="6 4 20 12 6 20 6 4"/></svg>
          Watch the Video
        </a>
      </div>
      <div class="way__media">
        <img src="/images/bible-school.jpg" alt="A Portable Bible School session in the field" loading="lazy" />
      </div>
    </article>

    <!-- 02 GIVING -->
    <article class="way" id="give">
      <div class="way__num">GIVING<strong>02</strong></div>
      <div class="way__body">
        <h3>Hold <em>the ropes</em>.</h3>
        <p>Hunger for the Word of God is immense, and Bibles are in short supply. Our 1,400 native missionaries lead with the spirit of the lay preachers and circuit riders of old, and they are preparing to travel to new villages and unreached people groups who have never heard the Gospel.</p>
        <p>The travel and living costs are significant. <strong>Can your church help?</strong></p>
        <div class="way__give-tiles">
          <div class="give-tile">
            <div class="give-tile__amt">$50</div>
            <div class="give-tile__what">Five Bibles in the hands of new believers.</div>
          </div>
          <div class="give-tile">
            <div class="give-tile__amt">$200<span style="font-size:14px;color:var(--ink-soft);font-weight:400;letter-spacing:0;">/mo</span></div>
            <div class="give-tile__what">Sponsor an indigenous missionary's ministry.</div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <a class="way__cta" href="https://favorintl.org/donate" target="_blank" rel="noopener">
          Give to Favor
          <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" aria-hidden="true"><path d="M5 12h14"/><path d="m12 5 7 7-7 7"/></svg>
        </a>
      </div>
      <div class="way__media">
        <img src="/images/field-men-shirts.jpg" alt="Indigenous missionaries gathered, ready to travel to new villages" loading="lazy" />
      </div>
    </article>

    <!-- 03 HOST -->
    <article class="way" id="host">
      <div class="way__num">HOST<strong>03</strong></div>
      <div class="way__body">
        <h3>Host <em>a Discover Favor Sunday</em>.</h3>
        <p>Schedule a presentation about Favor International with your staff or missions committee. Host a member of our team as a guest speaker for a <em>Discover Favor Sunday</em> — sharing the Word and testimony about this inspiring prayer and discipleship movement across Africa.</p>
        <p>Invite us to equip and strengthen your church's prayer ministry, and learn how we practice corporate prayer in Africa. We would be honored to be a part of your church's worship on a Sunday morning.</p>
        <div style="display:flex;flex-wrap:wrap;gap:10px;margin-top:8px;">
          <a class="way__cta" href="mailto:josh@favorintl.org?subject=Discover%20Favor%20Sunday%20—%20Inquiry%20from%20AECC&body=Hi%20Josh%2C%0A%0AOur%20church%20would%20like%20to%20discuss%20hosting%20you%20for%20a%20Discover%20Favor%20Sunday%20%2F%20presentation.%0A%0AChurch%3A%20%0AContact%3A%20%0APreferred%20dates%3A%20%0A%0AThanks%20for%20your%20heart%20for%20the%20nations.%0A">
            Email Josh
            <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" aria-hidden="true"><rect x="3" y="5" width="18" height="14" rx="2"/><path d="m3 7 9 6 9-6"/></svg>
          </a>
          <a class="way__cta way__cta--ghost" href="tel:+18133451005">
            <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" aria-hidden="true"><path d="M22 16.92v3a2 2 0 0 1-2.18 2 19.79 19.79 0 0 1-8.63-3.07 19.5 19.5 0 0 1-6-6 19.79 19.79 0 0 1-3.07-8.67A2 2 0 0 1 4.11 2h3a2 2 0 0 1 2 1.72 12.84 12.84 0 0 0 .7 2.81 2 2 0 0 1-.45 2.11L8.09 9.91a16 16 0 0 0 6 6l1.27-1.27a2 2 0 0 1 2.11-.45 12.84 12.84 0 0 0 2.81.7A2 2 0 0 1 22 16.92z"/></svg>
            Call · 813-345-1005
          </a>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="way__media">
        <img src="/images/banner-girls.jpg" alt="A celebration of children — fruit of the missionary partnership" loading="lazy" />
      </div>
    </article>
  </div>
</section>
